Corporate Overview




















(As of December 30.2015)


Company Name
Coca-Cola West  Co., Ltd.


Business Activities
Production and sale of Coca-Cola and other soft drinks


Head Office
7-9-66 Hakozaki, Higashi-ku, Fukuoka 812-8650, Japan


Management
Nobuo Shibata : Representative Director & Chairman
Tamio Yoshimatsu : Representative Director & President
Vikas Tiku : Director
Hiroyoshi Miyaki : Auditor (Full-time)
Gotaro Ichiki : Outside Auditor
Seiji Isoyama : Outside Auditor
Tomoko Ogami : Outside Auditor









